;Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.59,0:09:15.39,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喵~
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.85,0:09:19.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.46,0:09:23.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚了一步呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.09,0:09:25.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,叫他等等我们就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.01,0:09:28.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  真的被释放了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.47,0:09:29.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,证据不足嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.34,0:09:33.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过他也因为ZERO的事  被好好调查了一番
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.07,0:09:36.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎呀  怎么会…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.76,0:09:41.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不擅长和猫交流吗
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.78,0:09:43.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我倒是很喜欢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.55,0:09:48.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过总是我单恋
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.66,0:09:51.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会单恋的是很温柔的人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.27,0:09:55.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走掉了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.67,0:09:57.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤菲
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.15,0:10:00.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,刚才为什么撒那样的谎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.49,0:10:02.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在意我的事吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.54,0:10:04.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哎?  啊  是的…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.63,0:10:07.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就再陪陪我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.40,0:10:18.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这个样子
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.60,0:10:20.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和在布里塔尼亚的时候没什么不同呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.07,0:10:22.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤菲是从本国来的?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.38,0:10:24.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  是学生
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.48,0:10:25.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到上周为止还是
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.89,0:10:27.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,上周为止还是…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.28,0:10:28.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么现在呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.52,0:10:29.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,学生是指高中生?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.38,0:10:32.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想要观光的话什么时候都可以吧?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.50,0:10:34.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,问题好多呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.36,0:10:36.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  对不起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.94,0:10:38.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  我不是那个意思
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.39,0:10:42.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  因为今天是假期的最后一天
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.77,0:10:44.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以很想来看看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.64,0:10:45.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看看AREA-11
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.26,0:10:47.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里到底是怎么样的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.22,0:10:49.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话  不用找我也…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.79,0:10:52.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不  我很高兴是你
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.23,0:10:53.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.01,0:10:56.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.45,0:10:59.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能否请你再带我去一个地方呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.33,0:11:02.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,敬请吩咐  公主殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.34,0:11:04.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么 去新宿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.59,0:11:08.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请让我看一看新宿
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.26,0:11:10.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枢木朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.61,0:11:19.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鲁鲁修同学
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.43,0:11:21.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在方便吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.85,0:11:23.06,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  什么事?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.62,0:11:25.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,关于之前电话的事
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.25,0:11:26.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,电话?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.68,0:11:30.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个  就是在浴室的那次
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.51,0:11:34.28,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能不能查一下来电记录?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.66,0:11:36.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想和对方联系一下
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.26,0:11:37.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因为是学校的电话
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.96,0:11:38.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以我…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.71,0:11:41.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.98,0:11:43.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是啊  果然…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.93,0:11:45.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个女人…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.40,0:11:47.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么? 怎么了…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.69,0:11:48.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,发生什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.99,0:11:52.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.84,0:11:58.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.65,0:12:00.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这是什么意思
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.87,0:12:02.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  是什么意思呢?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.53,0:12:07.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然会以这种形式回本国
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.87,0:12:10.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当初不和那个女人扯上关系就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.13,0:12:13.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是笨蛋吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.54,0:12:14.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要到处乱逛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.10,0:12:16.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无所谓吧  反正是在学校内而已
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.41,0:12:18.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别说得那么严厉嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.89,0:12:19.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.97,0:12:21.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在这里可是个外人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.28,0:12:24.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在哪里都是一样的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.04,0:12:26.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个人在做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.36,0:12:29.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 今天也在做啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.09,0:12:30.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天也?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.08,0:12:38.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我对她使用了Geass  让她每天都来这墙上做标记
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.38,0:12:39.00,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Geass?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.45,0:12:40.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就是指这个力量
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.00,0:12:42.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在缔结契约的时候 我听到是这么叫的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.55,0:12:46.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在做关于持续时间的实验吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.66,0:12:48.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,武器的特性是应该要充分理解的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.33,0:12:51.09,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果你太任性的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.27,0:12:52.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对我会有效果吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.85,0:12:55.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.45,0:12:58.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你和我是共犯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.60,0:13:01.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不会做对我们不利的事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.28,0:13:09.64,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,新宿贫民区  已经完了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.71,0:13:12.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好不容易人们开始回到这个地方
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.15,0:13:23.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然 对付ELEVEN还不需要用到RG呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.27,0:13:26.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  这边有对人炮弹的痕迹
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.78,0:13:27.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,帮我拍照
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.85,0:13:28.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.96,0:13:29.86,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接着到我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.17,0:13:31.01,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.05,0:13:34.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的吗  关于ZERO的情报
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.79,0:13:36.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的  是丘威尔卿那里传来的消息
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.14,0:13:37.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很好
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.86,0:13:40.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,将新宿贫民区第四区域设置为紧急状态
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.90,0:13:42.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs20\fsp-1}{\fad(100,100)\a6)}[大公(Grand duke): 是西欧、尤其是日耳曼语族国家的爵位之一\N低于国王(King等)、高于公爵(Duke, Herzog，Furst等)]
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.90,0:13:42.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道了  大公
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.96,0:13:46.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丘威尔卿  之后就拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.32,0:13:51.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原本来这是想和杰雷米亚卿联系的
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.48,0:13:53.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不过看样子现在不是说这个的时候了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.13,0:13:55.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,给我滚出去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.98,0:13:57.03,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,布里塔尼亚的猪
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.29,0:13:59.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,待在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.50,0:14:00.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎  怎么了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.55,0:14:01.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只不过是ELEVEN嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.67,0:14:02.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是日本人!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.60,0:14:03.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不准叫ELEVEN!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.80,0:14:04.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在说什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.66,0:14:05.83,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你们输给我们了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.00,0:14:07.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战败国的狗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.70,0:14:09.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这个布里塔尼亚的混蛋!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.53,0:14:10.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请住手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.53,0:14:11.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要用暴力
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.60,0:14:12.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别妨碍我们!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.31,0:14:16.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.34,0:14:18.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你… 是枢木朱雀吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.47,0:14:21.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀了克洛维斯的枢木?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.44,0:14:22.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,笨蛋  是ZERO杀的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.01,0:14:25.73,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这家伙只是个奴隶而已
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.28,0:14:28.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么名誉布里塔尼亚人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.54,0:14:29.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,自己还一副高兴的样子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.06,0:14:32.22,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尊严  同伴  甚至连灵魂都出卖了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.44,0:14:33.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样还算是日本人吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.08,0:14:35.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不对!  我…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.41,0:14:36.40,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么不对的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.81,0:14:40.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这条布里塔尼亚的走狗!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.83,0:14:44.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请住手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.99,0:14:48.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是接受过训练的人
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.48,0:14:50.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不想再对同伴…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.12,0:14:52.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么同伴啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.36,0:14:53.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  已经够了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.45,0:14:57.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你这个叛徒
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.99,0:15:03.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱雀  没事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.71,0:15:05.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.08,0:15:07.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哪里没事了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.65,0:15:10.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我引以为傲的G-MX4啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.45,0:15:11.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你太慢了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.86,0:15:13.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  亏你还是个名誉布里塔尼亚人呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.12,0:15:15.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为什么让他们跑了?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.98,0:15:16.80,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杀了他们啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.12,0:15:19.32,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正你也杀了很多ELEVEN了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.63,0:15:21.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以为是谁在养你啊?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.87,0:15:27.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我绝不允许你再侮辱这个人!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.67,0:15:32.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要使用Geass 必须直视对方的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.79,0:15:35.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,眼镜这种程度的穿透没什么问题
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.44,0:15:38.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有效距离大约是270米左右
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.21,0:15:41.27,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,另外  被施予Geass的前后
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.46,0:15:42.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以及期间
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.62,0:15:44.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,会产生记忆缺损
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.75,0:15:49.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这可以认为是Geass介入大脑所造成的损伤
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.89,0:15:51.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果它是光信息的话
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.43,0:15:52.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反射也是可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.03,0:15:55.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那么短的时间内居然能调查到这个程度
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.63,0:16:00.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对手可是控制了世界三分之一以上的帝国啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.43,0:16:02.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再怎么谨慎也不为过
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.37,0:16:03.61,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是ELEVEN的话还能理解
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.89,0:16:05.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你是布里塔尼亚人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.27,0:16:07.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,仅仅凭借Geass去战斗的话
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.04,0:16:10.41,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对手未免也太强大了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.95,0:16:12.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要强大就好了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.31,0:16:16.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,弱小是不行的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.59,0:16:18.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.86,0:16:20.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在年仅10岁的我们看来
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.48,0:16:22.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,世界看起来非常的悲伤
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.04,0:16:25.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,饥饿
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.42,0:16:27.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,疾病
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.82,0:16:29.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,贪污  腐败
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.07,0:16:30.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歧视
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.23,0:16:32.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战争以及恐怖活动
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.23,0:16:35.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,重复不断的憎恨的连锁
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.82,0:16:38.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,愚蠢无谓的循环
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.98,0:16:42.25,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,必须有人来斩断这个连锁
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.15,0:16:44.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是理想
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.94,0:16:48.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,当然  我没有想过能让这一切全部消失
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.77,0:16:50.50,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我还没有傲慢到那个程度
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.99,0:16:51.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.99,0:16:54.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能够不失去最重要的人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.62,0:16:56.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,至少  一个没有战争的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.08,0:16:58.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那种理想的世界…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.31,0:17:00.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要怎么做…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.02,0:17:01.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很简单
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.56,0:17:04.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要某个人赢了的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.42,0:17:06.79,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,战争就能结束
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.70,0:17:08.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,某个人?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.47,0:17:11.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我自己也还不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.31,0:17:14.90,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是 如果放弃追求的话
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.14,0:17:16.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲就白白牺牲了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.43,0:17:18.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枢木首相吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.22,0:17:20.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那场战争中
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.84,0:17:22.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,父亲不得不死…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.83,0:17:27.46,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰雷米亚
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.76,0:17:30.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放任杀害克洛维斯殿下的凶手逃走
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.46,0:17:31.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这责任就用你的命来偿还吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.18,0:17:33.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卑鄙的丘威尔
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.81,0:17:35.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,说发现了ZERO是谎言吗
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.22,0:17:38.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在柯内莉娅殿下到任前
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.63,0:17:40.54,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一定要先清除内部的耻辱
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.93,0:17:42.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰雷米亚  这是肃清
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.94,0:17:46.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.12,0:17:47.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,塞希尔小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.14,0:17:49.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这里很危险  快上来
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.99,0:17:51.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,纯血派的内讧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.96,0:17:52.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,赶快逃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.37,0:17:54.19,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  还有
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.35,0:17:55.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你被无罪释放真是遗憾啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.08,0:17:57.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又要让你陪我们研究了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.82,0:17:58.47,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.93,0:18:02.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这不正是取得Lancelot战斗数据的好机会吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.78,0:18:05.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.92,0:18:06.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对不起  尤菲
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.23,0:18:08.44,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们就在这里分别吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.71,0:18:10.02,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不得不去
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.26,0:18:11.42,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果是Lancelot的话
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.66,0:18:12.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,应该可以阻止他们
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.55,0:18:14.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.20,0:18:17.70,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可恶
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.88,0:18:19.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然四个一起上
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.42,0:18:20.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,卑鄙小人
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.83,0:18:23.16,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放心吧  杰雷米亚
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.38,0:18:24.87,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对外会把你当成战死来处理
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.03,0:18:26.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不会让你家族的名誉受损的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.22,0:18:28.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是认真的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.65,0:18:30.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的要把我给…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.44,0:18:32.35,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丘威尔
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.58,0:18:33.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,闭嘴  ORANGE
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.70,0:18:35.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们是为了什么而存在的?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.89,0:18:37.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是为了皇室!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.68,0:18:41.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All Hail Britannia!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.23,0:18:46.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请住手
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.36,0:18:47.89,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,同为布里塔尼亚军的同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.23,0:18:50.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个是  名誉布里塔尼亚人的
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.80,0:18:52.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,向导兵器  Lancelot
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.52,0:18:56.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,特别派遣有何贵干?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.16,0:18:59.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,无论是谁  只要介入一律杀无赦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.72,0:19:00.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.23,0:19:05.07,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我无法坐视无意义的战斗而不加理会
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.32,0:19:09.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs20\fsp-1}{\fad(100,100)\a6)}[MVS：Maser Vibration Sword的缩写，镭射振动剑\N利用微波镭射振动制作的斩击用武器]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.32,0:19:09.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,MVS?  已经投入实战了吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.22,0:19:12.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是  事到如今 没有退路了!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.32,0:19:15.43,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明都是同伴 为什么…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.15,0:19:22.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,连我也救?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.84,0:19:24.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枢木朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.03,0:19:32.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话  即使只是杀死ORANGE也好…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.04,0:19:36.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,杰雷米亚卿
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.14,0:19:38.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs20\fsp-1}{\fad(100,100)\a6)}[维蕾塔·纽 Villetta Nu]
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.14,0:19:37.95,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,维蕾塔吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.04,0:19:38.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.94,0:19:43.20,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,还打算继续吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.48,0:19:47.12,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大家退后
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.85,0:19:49.49,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,丘威尔
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.79,0:19:50.93,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你终于能理解了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.46,0:19:53.85,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我要使用CHAOS爆雷
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.29,0:19:57.88,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请住手!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.80,0:19:59.34,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.06,0:20:23.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那个名誉布里塔尼亚人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.88,0:20:25.05,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,居然挺身涉险…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.64,0:20:27.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,双方都请收起手中的武器
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.40,0:20:32.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以我之名下令
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.97,0:20:34.30,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,难… 难道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.60,0:20:36.77,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是布里塔尼亚第三皇女
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.04,0:20:39.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fn黑体\fs20\fsp-1}{\fad(100,100)\a6)}[Euphemia Li Britannia]
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.04,0:20:39.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤菲米娅·Li·布里塔尼亚
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.30,0:20:41.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤菲?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.05,0:20:43.71,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,现在这里由我来指挥
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.07,0:20:44.99,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,全都退下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.74,0:20:48.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,果然是… 皇女殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.84,0:20:50.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是知道的吗?  罗伊德
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.76,0:20:52.92,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 因为是学生
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.03,0:20:55.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以不常抛头露面
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.57,0:20:57.24,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实… 实在是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.11,0:21:00.62,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,实在是罪该万死!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.99,0:21:02.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,皇女殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.46,0:21:05.66,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,虽然事先不知
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.89,0:21:06.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是请恕我先前失礼了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.48,0:21:10.15,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.80,0:21:12.76,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如同你失去了父亲一样
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.91,0:21:15.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也失去了兄长克洛维斯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.29,0:21:17.97,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,从今以后
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.24,0:21:20.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,为了创造不再失去重要之人的世界
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.17,0:21:22.82,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能否助我一臂之力呢
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.31,0:21:27.63,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是!  不胜荣幸
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.86,0:21:32.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我听说了  尤菲米娅
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.50,0:21:33.75,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,别太乱来哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.45,0:21:36.29,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,十分抱歉 皇姐
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.43,0:21:37.37,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.62,0:21:39.08,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在这种场合请叫我总督
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.32,0:21:40.57,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,尤菲米娅副总督
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.03,0:21:43.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,正因为我们是亲姐妹 所以更需要划清界限
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.01,0:21:45.58,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.64,0:21:49.55,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么  那边的情况怎样了?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.87,0:21:55.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是  在政厅已经准备好了盛大的宴会欢迎皇女殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.97,0:22:01.23,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,变得松懈  变得糊涂  变得堕落
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.70,0:22:02.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO的事怎样了!?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.15,0:22:05.04,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去逮捕帝国臣民的敌人
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.41,0:22:06.94,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,ZERO!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.94,0:22:10.56,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是从今天开始
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.77,0:22:13.52,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,转入这所阿斯福德学园学习的
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.02,0:22:15.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,枢木朱雀
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.51,0:22:16.96,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,请多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.72,0:23:50.68,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我明白的
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.22,0:23:52.59,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我在撒谎
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.99,0:23:54.26,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,对莎莉和利瓦尔他们
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.64,0:23:56.17,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,甚至连朱雀和娜娜莉也…
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.66,0:23:58.69,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是已经没有退路了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.07,0:23:59.74,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经无法回头了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.96,0:24:01.98,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,既然C.C.说是共犯的话
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.23,0:24:03.21,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就做共犯吧
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.92,0:24:06.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已经  不想对自己撒谎了
